<text top="106" left="113" width="2" height="9" font="0"> </text>
<text top="106" left="142" width="10" height="9" font="0">9. </text>
<text top="106" left="170" width="36" height="9" font="5"><i>Requests</i></text>
<text top="106" left="206" width="279" height="9" font="0"> the Secretary-General to give the Special Rapporteur all the human </text>
<text top="118" left="113" width="274" height="9" font="0">and financial assistance necessary for the fulfilment of the mandate. </text>
<text top="136" left="430" width="52" height="9" font="5"><i>57th meeting</i></text>
